{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/projects/figmacn/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"955c676d-25f9-5d89-9f07-e7bf94342573","excerpt":"最近迷上了 Figma——一款基于浏览器的在线协作工具。Figma 很多细节做的很棒，用一个朋友的话说，是很懂设计的人为设计师贴心打造的。为了方便更多国内设计师了解并使用这款设计软件，我自己设计并开发了 Figmacn.com。  目前，就我自己的使用体验来看，Figma…","html":"<p>最近迷上了 Figma——一款基于浏览器的在线协作工具。Figma 很多细节做的很棒，用一个朋友的话说，是很懂设计的人为设计师贴心打造的。为了方便更多国内设计师了解并使用这款设计软件，我自己设计并开发了 <a href=\"https://figmacn.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Figmacn.com</a>。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/a5d60019fa651c06f9b9532478afaabf/0b569/overview.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"网站概览\"\n        title=\"网站概览\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/a5d60019fa651c06f9b9532478afaabf/6af66/overview.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/a5d60019fa651c06f9b9532478afaabf/69538/overview.png 160w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/a5d60019fa651c06f9b9532478afaabf/72799/overview.png 320w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/a5d60019fa651c06f9b9532478afaabf/6af66/overview.png 640w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/a5d60019fa651c06f9b9532478afaabf/d9199/overview.png 960w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/a5d60019fa651c06f9b9532478afaabf/21b4d/overview.png 1280w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/a5d60019fa651c06f9b9532478afaabf/0b569/overview.png 2878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>目前，就我自己的使用体验来看，Figma 有以下特点吸引了我。</p>\n<h2>完全云端协作</h2>\n<p>最开始一直担心 Web 端的性能跟不上，没有原生应用那么顺滑。直到我使用了 Figma 才发现，这种担心完全是多余的。Figma 已经被打磨地很顺滑，而且会在网络条件不好时自动将改动保存在本地。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/361dcb38974cf99ef2f79a1c34e94c54/03680/web-based.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"基于 Web\"\n        title=\"基于 Web\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/361dcb38974cf99ef2f79a1c34e94c54/c08c5/web-based.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/361dcb38974cf99ef2f79a1c34e94c54/0913d/web-based.jpg 160w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/361dcb38974cf99ef2f79a1c34e94c54/cb69c/web-based.jpg 320w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/361dcb38974cf99ef2f79a1c34e94c54/c08c5/web-based.jpg 640w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/361dcb38974cf99ef2f79a1c34e94c54/6a068/web-based.jpg 960w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/361dcb38974cf99ef2f79a1c34e94c54/eea4a/web-based.jpg 1280w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/361dcb38974cf99ef2f79a1c34e94c54/03680/web-based.jpg 1652w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>当性能不再成为瓶颈，云端应用的优点就显现出来了。首先是跨平台，<strong>不需要下载安装，不限操作系统，只需要在浏览器输入链接就能进入自己的工作区</strong>。其次，所有文件存在云端，不用费神管理一堆本地文件了。最后，Web 端便与传播的特性使得交付变得简单，<strong>只需要将链接给其他人，查看标注、实时评论都很方便</strong>。</p>\n<h2>更加符合直觉的组件</h2>\n<p>Sketch 的 Symbol 我一直觉得有几个地方不合理，首先是只能通过 Symbol Overrides 来改变样式，这意味着你要不断给 Symbol 增加可能的状态。如果只有一个 Symbol 的实例需要做一些不同的样式，就只能将这个 Symbol 拆卸（Detach）了。而 Figma 则完全不同，组件实例有一些属性是不能改变的，但有一部分属性是可以改变的。这意味着，你可以保持各个组件实例能够和 master 保持一致的同时，又能够对其中某个实例做一些变动，通过下图感受一下。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/ece77cbae1e7ad2ba476ae9dbeb393f5/component.gif\" alt=\"组件\"></p>\n<p>还有一点是 Sketch 的 Symbol 必须要进入 Symbol 编辑模式才可以编辑，而 Figma 的组件可以放在页面的任何地方。这样就很方便，因为我可能要随时根据当前设计来更改组件。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/68f5d57aaef64beea2104b0e68dddffa/20b4c/nearby-components.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"就近放置组件\"\n        title=\"就近放置组件\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/68f5d57aaef64beea2104b0e68dddffa/c08c5/nearby-components.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/68f5d57aaef64beea2104b0e68dddffa/0913d/nearby-components.jpg 160w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/68f5d57aaef64beea2104b0e68dddffa/cb69c/nearby-components.jpg 320w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/68f5d57aaef64beea2104b0e68dddffa/c08c5/nearby-components.jpg 640w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/68f5d57aaef64beea2104b0e68dddffa/6a068/nearby-components.jpg 960w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/68f5d57aaef64beea2104b0e68dddffa/eea4a/nearby-components.jpg 1280w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/68f5d57aaef64beea2104b0e68dddffa/20b4c/nearby-components.jpg 1504w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>其他小细节</h2>\n<p>还有其他的一些小细节，比如文字的颜色没有单独拿出来，而是使用填充色来调整。这样是很方便的，因为我经常需要同时更改一个图层和文字的颜色。在其它设计软件中就只能分开更改文字颜色和图层颜色了。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/c014221f454c50613b957e632db8d08c/9657e/fill.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"就近放置组件\"\n        title=\"就近放置组件\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/c014221f454c50613b957e632db8d08c/c08c5/fill.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/c014221f454c50613b957e632db8d08c/0913d/fill.jpg 160w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/c014221f454c50613b957e632db8d08c/cb69c/fill.jpg 320w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/c014221f454c50613b957e632db8d08c/c08c5/fill.jpg 640w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/c014221f454c50613b957e632db8d08c/6a068/fill.jpg 960w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/c014221f454c50613b957e632db8d08c/9657e/fill.jpg 1216w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>诸如此类的细节还有很多，这让我对 Figma 好感倍增。目前，我已经使用 Figma 作为自己的主力设计工具，如果你想更深入地了解 Figma，可以前往 <a href=\"https://figmacn.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Figmacn.com</a>。</p>\n<h3>参考</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/6lPT_9NQmqwVYOlaL0NkEw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">如何使用 Figma 来完成你的设计工作流</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/PoEk5vRRrquLOTOH3QZgIw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Figma 最佳实践：组件、样式和共享库（上）</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/FsuuJBXr3es9D2Yg-NZP9g\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">在 Figma 中如何选择 group（组）或 frame（画框）？</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/dvgyO_lh7XvjjoImo1hIxw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">使用 Figma 完成产品设计工作流</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Figma 中文网","date":"2018/11/05","description":"最近迷上了 Figma——一款基于浏览器的在线协作工具。Figma 很多细节做的很棒，用一个朋友的话说，是很懂设计的人为设计师贴心打造的。","color":"#131313","cover":"figmacn.jpg","demo":"https://figmacn.com","demoText":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/projects/figmacn/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/tools/movielect/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"如果你想看电影，却不知道看什么"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/creative/find-two-elephants/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"不就是找对象嘛，我一分钟能找 100 个"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454"]}